description: [Fresh Class A basted whole chicken seasoned with Piri Piri. Without giblets., Why wait until the weekend for a roast? Our oven ready whole British chicken is so easy to cook, simply roast in the bag for tender chicken and less mess at mealtimes. This succulent centrepiece is seasoned with piri piri for a spicy twist and a completely fuss free family meal.  Serve this low fuss family favourite with a summery salad and corn on the cob and try our five star rated Real Food Provençale peppers recipe. For a crispier skin try basting with the cooking juices after opening the bag. Return to the oven and cook for a further 5 10 minutes.  Click on the Recipes tab at the top of this webpage to see our Real Food chicken recipes with ingredients you can add straight to your basket.  Our Tesco chicken is sourced solely from British supplying farms which meet the Red Tractor standards along with our own strict Livestock Codes of Practice. These chickens, are reared in houses with windows that provide natural daylight. In addition, they are also provided with environmental benefits such as bales and perches. Studies have shown this type of enrichment improves the activity and wellbeing of the birds.  For recipe inspiration and to see how we work with farmers visit realfood.tesco.com.]
